headline: Commvault Systems (CVLT) Beats Q3 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Commvault (CVLT) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +19.39% and +4.96%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
